<br>
5% haste is HUGE.  Esp. the difference between 16% and 21%.  A 5% increase in speed at 16% is a 31% increase in haste.  Kinda like one delay off an 17 delay weapon is huge, but one delay off of a 50 delay isn't as much.  Going from 16% to 21% is a large percent increase in speed.  <br>
<br>
Now think about a CoF.  People will spend 10's of thousands of pp to get a little more haste.  <br>
<br>
You think adding 20 ac will help you more then 5% haste?  I bet you could kill a mob with less damage overall and faster with the 5% haste over 20 more ac.  <br>
<br>
You are fooling yourself is you don't think that 21% haste is much much better then 16% haste.  Paladins weak link is damage output, thats the are that needs most attention to make pallys a complete class.  If wer aren't tanking, then are damage is what we are contributing, besides our second rate spells. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukeynsoulfighter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keyn Soulfighter</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 378<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/31/02 9:52:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=344.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://jbob147.homestead.com/files/bar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: FBSS or Belt of Virtue?</span><hr size=1> i tell you what.. im gonna play how i play.. and you do whatever floats your boat?  mmm k?<br>
